data.description: If you are looking for a move-in-ready POOL home that offers beautiful WATER VIEWS and lots of space in a wonderful neighborhood, this is the one! Located in the desirable gated community of the Estates of Auburndale, this home is situated on a .29 acre corner lot leading to a cul-de-sac. With stone details, a side-loading garage, crisp exterior paint and an attractive front elevation, this home boasts excellent curb appeal. As you enter through the foyer, you will be impressed first and foremost by the breathtaking WATER VIEWS enjoyed through the sliding glass doors! With high ceilings, crown molding, and decorative touches throughout, such as archways and transom windows, this home makes a fantastic first impression. The functional triple-split floor plan includes formal and informal areas for both living and dining, making it excellent for anyone who enjoys entertaining. You will love the open kitchen with upgrades such as granite countertops, stainless-steel appliances, and beautiful wood cabinets. The master has its own private en-suite bathroom, with his-and-her walk-in-closets, separate dual vanities, garden tub, shower, and water closet. Off of the large family room are two bedrooms, and access to the pool bathroom. The pool bathroom exterior door is within the pool screen and patio, making it very convenient when enjoying time outside! There is an additional private bathroom downstairs, as well as a large room that would make a wonderful office or 4th bedroom. Upstairs there is a  bonus room with its own full bathroom, a perfect flex-space if you need a playroom, additional office or a 5th bedroom. Outside, you will love the screened-in pool and covered patio area, all overlooking the beautiful pond! If you need storage, this home has ample options, with walk-in closets in most of the bedrooms, a HUGE storage area under the stairs, a fantastic kitchen pantry, and many additional closets throughout. A spacious private laundry room is another feature you will appreciate, with additional storage, as well. This home has newer carpet and laminate flooring, newer central vacuum system, and the primary downstairs A/C system was replaced in 2018. In this well-kept community, you will enjoy amenities such as community pools, a playground, and sidewalks. With a convenient location near I-4 and the Polk Parkway, this home offers a wonderful quality of life for anyone looking to enjoy all that Central Florida has to offer!
